            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>For fancy presentation, cut the <strong>peppered salami </strong>in half and roll each half into cone-shapes</p><p>Roll the<strong> Napoli salami</strong> into tubes and cut in half</p><p>Tip: Too fiddly? Just break both up into smaller pieces!</p><p>Tear the <strong>Serrano ham </strong>into smaller pieces and add to a serving board with the <strong>Napoli salami</strong> and<strong> salami cones </strong>– this is your<strong> charcuterie</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
