          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> </strong>potatoes are fork tender, add them to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Bash the<strong> potatoes </strong>with a<strong> rolling pin</strong>, or crush them with a fork</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
